.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE_LIST_BY_LABEL" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-list-by-label \- list invoices matching a label prefix
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-list-by-label
.I label_prefix
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns invoices whose label starts with the given prefix.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
